\newlabel{fig:importance}{{5}{5}{Random Forest feature importances. \texttt {Days\_Since\_Last\_Login}, \texttt {Monthly\_Spend}, and \texttt {Age} dominate; one-hot encoded categorical features contribute little individually}{figure.5}{}}
